79
0:03:43.105,000 --> 0:03:44,000
(Laughter)

80
0:03:44.953,000 --> 0:03:46,000
What's the more likely explanation?

81
0:03:47,000 --> 0:03:49,000
Before we say something is out of this world,

82
0:03:49.191,000 --> 0:03:51,000
