83
0:03:51.879,000 --> 0:03:52,000
What's more likely:

84
0:03:53.054,000 --> 0:03:56,000
that Arnold had extraterrestrial help in his run for the governorship,

85
0:03:56.404,000 --> 0:03:58,000
